# Exhibit #003: *Humblebragus Maximus*

**Common Name:** The Humblebrag Peacock

### Observation
This species has mastered the ancient art of disguising bragging as self-deprecation.

### Natural Habitat
LinkedIn, Instagram captions, and WhatsApp status.

### Mating Call
"Just a small startup I built in my free time" (while posting a picture in front of a Lamborghini)

### Conservation Status
**Extremely Common in Urban Areas**

### Curator's Note
One of the most sophisticated mammals in the zoo. Their ability to sound humble while flexing is truly remarkable.
